name: Momo
description: Momo Is The First Female Shiba Inu, and she has brought her energy to Solana. A community-led memecoin that survived early abandonment and was rebuilt by holders into a true movement, and one of the few remaining ethical memecoins. Powered by an incredibly active community and transparent leadership, Momo channels creator fees into real-world utility, including support for charitable and social causes. Momo stands for long-term sustainability, honest building, and positive impact. This community will never stop until people are put first in Crypto again.
